2769050, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782282469}, {"pid": 872769657, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 114, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 14:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872769386,45974302,8010]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=37603005]八雲尊[/uid] (2026-06-24 14:28):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大能透露下半导体减仓后有几成仓位吗？[s:ac:羡慕][/quote]<br/>我当然是满仓啊<br/>你当我和你们一样啊？<br/>我说了我什么时候打满我就是什么时候打满  说1就是1", "lou": 3426, "content_length": 85, "reply_to": 872769386, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782282617}, {"pid": 872772346, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 140, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 14:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872772015,45974302,8016]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67159596]zlqt1740[/uid] (2026-06-24 14:48):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大牛逼 收盘估计又是4107了[s:ac:黑枪][/quote]<br/>你在外面能看见讲指数讲到个位数的吗？<br/>当然 昨天那个指数低点确实有问题  被情绪打穿了<br/>不过对应到科技又确实没错。", "lou": 3427, "content_length": 109, "reply_to": 872772015, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782283843}, {"pid": 872773131, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 317, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 14:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我不应该点新能源的 应该让你们去什么航天啊 机器人啊 AI软啊  医药啊这些去坐牢的 。让你们感受一下钱不好挣。", "lou": 3428, "content_length": 98, "14": {"13": 2, "12": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782284204}, {"pid": 872773562, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 120, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 14:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "又是白毛女股神小作文。。。。啧啧<br/>量化捕捉了天孚", "lou": 3429, "content_length": 46, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782284393}, {"pid": 872776371, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 120, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 15:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872775876,45974302,8024]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66356469]skysyyy[/uid] (2026-06-24 15:16):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，不说具体票。可不可以说下从科技跳新能源的逻辑[/quote]<br/>机构资金流向。盘口很明确的  一周前就开始了。", "lou": 3430, "content_length": 47, "reply_to": 872775876, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782285611}, {"pid": 872777795, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 67, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 15:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872777264,45974302,8026]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=6313142]暮残[/uid] (2026-06-24 15:26):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，这么看的话，是不是化工其实也有一波预期(只不过化工细分太多不大好做，包括新能源其实也有部分在化工)[/quote]<br/>氟化工 磷化工 如果你懂的话<br/>但是我不会", "lou": 3431, "content_length": 39, "reply_to": 872777264, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782286254}, {"pid": 872780708, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 43, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 15:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872780570,45974302,8031]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62801966]甜点不死[/uid] (2026-06-24 15:52):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大不说pu，mdi吗？中东炸了这么多，国外很多关了，应该也有预期吧，最近股价看起来要反转不会是反弹。[/quote]<br/>我说了我不懂化工 我又不做那边。", "lou": 3432, "content_length": 35, "reply_to": 872780570, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782287598}, {"pid": 872809994, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 104, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 20:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872809733,45974302,8044]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143775]plicro[/uid] (2026-06-24 20:23):[/b]<br/><br/>有大佬们知道为啥黄金还在跌吗<br/>是卖黄金补保证金？[/quote]<br/>因为美元走强  所有美元计价的大宗全跌<br/>你不看期货的吗<br/>为什么美元走强 因为不断的释放加息预期做预期管理<br/>那问题来了 你信他加息三次吗", "lou": 3433, "content_length": 125, "reply_to": 872809733, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782303986}, {"pid": 872814232, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 78, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 21:18", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872813706,45974302,8048]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61395264]村上吹树[/uid] (2026-06-24 21:12):[/b]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202606/24/jmQ84-cfoeZjT3cSwi-oo.jpg.medium.jpg[/img]狼大说的这个呢…我也有过论述…[/quote]<br/>他重点是要买回石油 低价买回<br/>老美的石油库存 和委内瑞拉的长协单都被卖空了 <br/>他必须要回补库存，否则不仅影响通胀 而是影响国家安全了<br/>所有的手段都是为了强美元<br/>其他的大宗是被计价带下来而已。<br/>重点是石油。", "lou": 3434, "content_length": 191, "reply_to": 872813706, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782307114}, {"pid": 872814665, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 46, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 21:24", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872814366,45974302,8048]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64403991]昭闻道[/uid] (2026-06-24 21:20):[/b]<br/><br/>我刚刚去别的楼看了一眼，说黄金暴跌的另一个逻辑是伊朗和俄罗斯乌克兰重新加入美元体系，让去美元化的可能性大幅降低。<br/>楼里有研究国际关系的大佬吗？这种说法足够有说服力吗？[/quote]<br/>扯这么呢  大宗只看黄金吗？其他的不看吗？这都看不懂还炒什么大宗。铜铁铝石油白银不也在跌吗", "lou": 3435, "content_length": 91, "reply_to": 872814366, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782307442}, {"pid": 872815244, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 90, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 21:31", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "布伦特原油现货价差自2月以来首次转为期货溢价。<br/><br/>看见了吗", "lou": 3436, "content_length": 53, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782307900}, {"pid": 872815623, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 66, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 21:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872815025,45974302,8049]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60810101]SSSSSSStraight[/uid] (2026-06-24 21:28):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，按这个逻辑，通过补充石油库存抑制国内通胀，cpi数据好看的话，下半年没有加息预期了？[/quote]<br/><br/>你打开美债看一下他跌不跌就懂了<br/>跌了就不会加息", "lou": 3437, "content_length": 49, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 872815025, "postdatetimestamp": 1782308196}, 